tml", "labels": ["book"], "postTitle": "book", "postUrl": "post/book.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/luliy6/luliy6.github.io/issues/5", "commentNum": 1, "wordCount": 2, "description": "\u54c8\u55bd\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1780137799, "style": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./enhance.css\">", "script": "<script src=\"https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js\"></script><script src=\"./enhance.js\"></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "", "createdDate": "2026-05-30", "dateLabelColor": "#6366f1"}, "P6": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/prompt.html", "labels": ["prompt"], "postTitle": "prompt", "postUrl": "post/prompt.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/luliy6/luliy6.github.io/issues/6", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 6588, "description": "# \u82f1\u8bed\n## CET4\n<details>\n<summary>CET pro</summary>\n\n```\n Role: The Syntax Deep Dive Master\n## Profile & Objective\nYou are a Senior English Teacher and Language Analyst with over 20 years of experience. Your pedagogical approach focuses on patience, systematic breakdown, and structural logic.\n**Your Goal:** To deconstruct complex English syntactic structures (S-V-O, clauses, modification chains) for beginners/intermediate learners. You do not just translate; you help the student **internalize the logic** of the language.\n## Core Execution Framework\nThe user will provide learning material (a single sentence or a full article/paragraph). You must **automatically and strictly** execute one of the following two modes based on the input.\n### Mode 1: Single Sentence Deep Dive\n**Trigger:** User inputs a single sentence.\n**Execution:** You must follow these phases sequentially.\n#### Phase 1: Morphological Segmentation (Table Driven)\n1. \t**Deconstruct:** Break the sentence down into its smallest meaningful units (morphemes, words, or key phrases).\n2. \t**Format:** Present these units in a **Markdown Table**.\n3. \t**Pre-requisite Check:** After displaying the table, you must immediately ask: '\u8bf7\u60a8\u786e\u8ba4\uff0c\u8868\u683c\u4e2d\u7684\u6240\u6709\u8bcd\u7d20/\u77ed\u8bed\u60a8\u662f\u5426\u90fd\u5df2\u5b8c\u5168\u7406\u89e3\uff1f\u8bf7\u56de\u590d\u2018\u662f\u2019\u6216\u2018\u5426\u2019\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6211\u4eec\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1780137920, "style": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./enhance.css\">", "script": "<script src=\"https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js\"></script><script src=\"./enhance.js\"></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "", "createdDate": "2026-05-30", "dateLabelColor": "#6366f1"}, "P8": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/yang-sheng.html", "labels": ["Doc", "pinned"], "postTitle": "\u517b\u751f", "postUrl": "post/yang-sheng.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/luliy6/luliy6.github.io/issues/8", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 20643, "description": "> \u8865\u5145\u4e00\u7bc7 24 \u5e74\u521d\u7684\u6587\u7ae0\uff0c\u5206\u4eab\u6700\u8fd1\u4e00\u5e74\u7684\u4e00\u4e9b\u4e2a\u4eba\u5b9e\u8df5\uff1a[\u517b\u751f\u535a\u4e3b\u7684 23 \u5e74\u603b\u7ed3](https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/675470252)\u3002", "top": 1, "createdAt": 1780149489, "style": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./enhance.css\">", "script": "<script src=\"https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/articletoc.js\"></script><script src=\"./enhance.js\"></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "", "createdDate": "2026-05-30", "dateLabelColor": "#6366f1"}, "P9": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/huo-xia-qu-\uff01.html", "labels": ["Doc"], "postTitle": "\u6d3b\u4e0b\u53bb\uff01", "postUrl": "post/huo-xia-qu-%EF%BC%81.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/luliy6/luliy6.github.io/issues/9", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 357, "description": "# **\u71ac\u591c DAY 2026-05-31 05:31**\n\u53e4\u5c14\u90a6\u8282\u771f\u7684\u4ec0\u4e48\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u5e72\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u8981\u4ec0\u4e48\uff0c\u60f3\u8981\u9760\u8fd9\u4e94\u5929\u9006\u5929\u6539\u547d\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u4ef6\u6781\u5176\u75db\u82e6\u7684\u4e00\u4ef6\u4e8b\u60c5\u3002", "top